{"tid":2062814,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"隨著日本各地學校復課，來自10至19歲少女的懷孕相談在急增，其中還有小學生的個案","createTime":"2020-06-13T11:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T13:10:36.000Z","uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc34f21d26f2eecd727f7b9b640204e8385bcf1","tid":2062814,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"【真的ヤバい】隨著日本各地學校復課，來自10至19歲少女的懷孕相談在急增，其中還有小學生的個案<br />\n<br />\n有24小時相談服務的保健師表示，以往該服務收到10至19歲的個案只佔約3成，但現時比率已高達7成，當中最年輕的是一位小學四年生，打後還有幾個小學六年生的個案...<br />\n<br />\n據說日本女生的初潮大約落在10-15歲這個範圍，而根據wiki有關的記載：<br />\n<br />\n//初潮代表子宮內膜受到雌激素刺激而發育了，也代表從子宮到子宮頸到陰道的「通路」打開了。<br />\n<br />\n初潮以及隨後的月經可能並不和排卵一起發生。但也有在初潮之前一至兩週排卵的罕見例子。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/436973393144376/posts/1608217406019963/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F436973393144376%2Fposts%2F1608217406019963%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=87195491\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/436973393144376/posts/1608217406019963/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee7b250201014836ed254dc36d1af8736ef29bf","tid":2062814,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7020f734d9ae6507eaaa2caac3b56bf15e34d1b","tid":2062814,"uid":42340,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"好想係屌日本妹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hk